FINAL RECOMMENDATION
=====================

EXACT PROBLEM STATEMENT (derived from research): 

"xAI's Colossus has 100K+ H100 GPUs creating synchronized power swings of 100+ MW.
Tesla Megapacks and Autobidder are connected REACTIVELY — they respond AFTER spikes.
No software layer exists that PREDICTS GPU power demand 10 minutes ahead and
PROACTIVELY signals batteries to pre-charge/discharge before grid instability."

BEST SOLUTION APPROACH:

